node.text:
Wow Ethan looks like his dad
.
🤍 Ace - Staying with Max and helping out with Jorani’s restaurant, as well as trying fast food for the first time opened his eyes. Now that he has to provide for himself, he’s gotten a lot more careful about holding his tongue in many situations. In the past, his family would sweep it under the rug for him. He’s moved from bragging about himself to bragging about his two daughters.
.
💚 Ivana - Someone come get their mom 🤸‍♂️ She thought about teaching English at one point, but was encouraged by her husband to write the books she’s always wanted to write instead. He promised to take care of everything else, so she took the offer. Her kids sometimes scold her for occasionally slacking off at home to watch Netflix, but she will defend herself by saying it’s research for her genre.
.
❤️ Max - He has successfully resisted all his family’s pestering to join the company, and tried pursuing a career in some form of physical activity. During his backup dancer era, he has appeared in some music videos of prevalent artists in this universe. He doesn’t really mention that fact unless you bring it up first, but that’s something that happened in his life at one point. 
.
💜 Dylan - If the professor doesn’t show up in 15 minutes, you’re legally allowed to leave. Yet somehow he always makes it last minute, just like his grading, which can stress some students out. He lets his students call him by his first name, and he generally has a very informal relationship with them.
.
💖 Ethan - Let me explain Neversea: Someone in his band told him that his personality is most like Peter Pan’s, since they were on the topic of fictional characters anyway. Ethan’s thought process went from “Peter Pan -> Neverland ……Land. Land and sea? ……NEVERSEA” It took the whole night to convince him not to make this change
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.

I have decided to post ✨whenever I feel like it✨ and it feels so much better this way 👁v👁 I’ll make a speedpaint of this for Patreon at some point this month!
.
Panicky pastel girl x Lanky weed boy actually have parallels to ships I like 👀👀 They would have English, PE and chemistry class together:
.
✏️ Ivana would be writing these detailed ass notes with all the washi tape and stickers. Cried internally when the teacher moves onto the next slide too fast. She looks over to see what Dylan wrote, and all she sees is blank paper. He’s probably napping or staring ahead with a half a (sleepy) smile on. His usual papers are nowhere near as thorough as Ivana’s, but his best ones come from when he’s high as a kite.
.
🏀 Ivana would suck at all the sports and be out of breath really quickly. Dylan would walk on all the miles no matter what and also get tired fast. They would both be suffering together 
.
🧪 This is the class that Ivana hates but Dylan likes. If they were lab partners, she would have to stop him from mixing chemicals he shouldn’t. His reasoning is just “haha prettee colors-“
.
What do you think they’d be like together?
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.

node.text:
Kpop AU! 🕺🕺 And I’m sorry Jackson ily 💔
.
.
Boutta throw some fancy terminology that I only recently learned about this year 💃 In kpop, each member usually has multiple roles in their group. Being a lead and being a main are not the same thing! The mains are the most capable at their skill, so are given the most difficult parts of that type of performance. Leads are still amazing at what they do, but may have parts that lead into the mains’ instead.
.
.
❤️Max would be a main dancer & a lead vocalist. Out of the 6 or 7 members, he’s the 2nd youngest with Ace being the youngest. He is a bit of a secret perfectionist over little mistakes made with his dancing. He’ll rehearse by himself so that none of the other members see that, but they all know what he’s doing 🤡 Fans adore his shy side which will occasionally come up. [Singing VC: Jackson Wang]
.
🤍 Ace would be the face of the group, lead dancer, main vocalist, and the meanest maknae to exist (probably has a lot of managers watching his ass so he doesn’t cross a line). He answers to both Ace (stage name) and Yunseok (real name). Takes a LOT of pride in being the face of the group, and can hit the high notes pretty well. [Singing VC: Vincent Blue]
.
.
❤️🤍 Max and Ace dorm together and bicker constantly. The group’s management team is still in the process of making little mascots for the members (like BT21), and Ace is INSISTING that they make Max’s mascot a melon headed boy. Totally not because he calls his head a fat melon all the time. Who knows if he’ll be listened to tho, since this is not the first time he’s made demands like this 💩
.
Ethan was going to be in this band too, but I decided that he should be an independent artist who collabs with them instead. Dylan would be his manager. Ivana would work with Max and Ace though, being their makeup artist. 
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
